  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math><mroot><mrow><mn>50</mn><mi>n</mi></mrow><mn>4</mn></mroot><msup><mfenced><mroot><mrow><mn>50</mn><mi>n</mi></mrow><mn>6</mn></mroot></mfenced><mn>3</mn></msup></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For what value of <em>x</em> is the given expression equivalent to <math><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>50</mn><mi>n</mi></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mn>24</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup></math>, where <em>n</em> &gt; 1?</p>",
